code class=3D"argument">V</code>,
                where <code class=3D"argument">sigma</code> specifies the s=
tandard deviation of the Gaussian
                smoothing filter. <code class=3D"literal">edge3</code> choo=
ses the size of the filter
                automatically, based on <code class=3D"argument">sigma</cod=
e>.</p></div></div><div class=3D"description_element"><div class=3D"code_re=
sponsive"><p><span id=3D"d126e104585" itemprop=3D"syntax"><code class=3D"sy=
